WorkItem.Description:
Use this code to fill tree in "Simple Sample" and enable Virtualization.
```
var firstNode = new Node { Name = "element" };
for (int i = 1; i <= 3; i++)
{
    var first = new Node { Name = "element" + i };
    for (int j = 1; j <= 50; j++)
        first.Children.Add(new Node { Name = "element" + i + "_" + j });
    firstNode.Children.Add(first);
}
```
